               <head>Two works on cosmology</head>
               <msContents class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008101799">
                  <summary>Two works on cosmology. Amateurish quasi-naskhī. 12 lines. Paginated: [1], 114 and [1], 49 pages. 84 folios. 21 x 15 cm. Plastic binding, imitation red and black half leather. Purchased from Mr. N.A. Majnoon, 8 January 2010. </summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85033176" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Or_16783-item1">
                     <locus from="2v" to="58v">ff. 2v-58v</locus>
                     <note>
                        <p>A brief treatise on cosmology, comprising 36 sections called ṣaḥīfa. Apparently unpublished.
</p>
                        <p>Dated 7.12.1352/27 February 1974 on 2r and 58v. Copied by <persName key="person_f7036" role="scr">ʿAbd al-Ṣamad</persName> (colophon, 56r).
                        </p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="per">Persian</textLang>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_22153">Kitāb-i ṣaḥīfah</title>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85033176 " n="2" xml:id="Uk_Or_16783-item2">
                     <locus from="59r" to="83v">ff. 59r-83v</locus>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_22154">Zubdat al-maʿānī</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Another brief treatise, on aspects of cosmology and spiritual life, titled <title>Zabīdat al-maʿāʾinī</title> for <title>Zubdat al-maʿānī</title>. Apparently unpublished.
                        </p>
                        <p>Copied in Kabul and dated 25.1.1354/14 April 1975, by <persName key="person_f7472" role="scr">Pīr Naẓar valad-i Pīr Muḥammad</persName>. 
                        </p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="per">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
